@startuml development_workflow
title Tark-Vitark Development Workflow (High Level)

skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

start

:Session Bootstrap;
note right
Load in order:
1. AGENTS.md
2. docs/current-state.md
3. docs/non-functional-requirements-baseline.md
4. docs/functional-requirements-index.md
5. Active slice specs
6. docs/decision-log.md
end note

:Plan Gate;
note right
- Scope and acceptance criteria
- Requirements spec + index update
- Baseline NFR inheritance
- Issue creation/update
end note

:UX Gate;
note right
- UX spec in repo
- Figma link or explicit waiver
- Accessibility and responsive expectations
end note

:Build Gate;
note right
- Implement approved slice
- Keep FR traceability in PR/tests
- Respect non-goals and boundaries
end note

:Review Gate;
note right
- Quality verification
- Code stewardship
- Regression and acceptance checks
end note

if (Risk-sensitive change?) then (yes)
  :Risk Gate;
  note right
  Security and/or Release checks
  end note
endif

:Ship Gate;
note right
- Required approvals
- Merge/release decision
end note

:Write-through Persistence;
note right
Update in same task:
- docs/current-state.md
- docs/functional-requirements-index.md
- Active slice FR/UX specs
- docs/decision-log.md
end note

:Next Slice;
stop

@enduml
